heading.headline: JMSS Time
heading.byline: Modernisation and feature development for a prexisting online timetable.

post.content: JMSS Time was a website originally created in 2017, with the simple aim of letting [John Monash Science School](https://jmss.vic.edu.au) students know when their classes are. Collective Fullstack were brought in to update the website for the timetable introduced in 2020, as well to add new features.
post.title: JMSS Time

images.alt: A specially designed weekly timetable view for online learning requirements during the 2020 Covid-19 lockdown
